00:57:03,864 --> 00:57:06,706
[SPEAKER_17]: They were truly a family-owned business, Mr. President.

848
00:57:07,627 --> 00:57:11,970
[SPEAKER_17]: If you didn't have the money to pay for an item, they put you what was called the cuff.

