00:57:45,059 --> 00:57:46,260
[SPEAKER_17]: And he really cared.

855
00:57:46,280 --> 00:57:48,882
[SPEAKER_17]: He didn't just ask and didn't wait for an answer.

856
00:57:49,242 --> 00:57:50,683
